Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:22.97,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈妈 我不是妈妈的女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:30.82,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是妈妈的朋友和一个来港口\N做爵士歌手的病弱美国大兵生的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:35.16,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又没有同性朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:38.32,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说这也不是一个小孩子该说的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.89,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:46.47,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绪花啊 你知道小孩子从哪儿来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:48.47,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起从卷心菜田里捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:50.85,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我更喜欢送子鹳叼来的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:52.41,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:55.23,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从田里把小孩子挖出来也太扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.32,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕 是催稿的 你去接 你去接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:00.28,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:01.96,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快去接
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:03.96,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手还湿着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:05.29,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 这里是松前家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.69,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好 是你男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.13,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呀 抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:16.11,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经不行了啦 被编辑催的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:17.23,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天过来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:20.70,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诶？有话说的话过来边喝酒边聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:22.67,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做好晚饭等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:24.46,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绪花做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.45,SCREEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,370)}十\N六\N岁\N\N春\N天\N\N含\N苞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.45,SCREEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(763,371)}、\N\N\N\N、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.10,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有问题问小孝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:35.71,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么才能吃到玉米？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:39.31,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}易拉罐里面的玉米都粘住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这样好难看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.06,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 吃不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}灌点水进去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:54.13,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真奇怪 那多难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:57.16,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样和吃不到玉米也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…把玉米汁倒进另一个杯子里 用筷子把玉米夹出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.57,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这么性急的一个人 居然想出这么迂回的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:17.95,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孝~小孝~慢性子呀~慢性子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你二年级的选修课选什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.84,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唔…没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将来什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.88,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不想定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真是散漫成性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样下去会自毁前途的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.44,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自毁前途什么的也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:40.88,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}挺戏剧性的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:48.16,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无趣的景色 被楼房遮住的小小的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:54.86,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乘着拥挤的电车 一时逃离被染成橙色的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么啊 不是很有型么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.17,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里有型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:05.84,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎么说我还是挺现实的 毕竟和反面教材生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你妈妈也真是了不起呢 好多事情上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.91,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就算不急着决定好未来的路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:16.00,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也会找一份稳定的工作 到26岁左右结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:19.27,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老了以后在三丁目的陵园买一块墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我爸说那里的墓地貌似挺贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不努力赚钱的话就买不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.75,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出局了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 春假你有什么安排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.62,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没…没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.28,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是一天中我唯一喜欢的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:08.11,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}灯光一点点亮起来 为我照亮前行的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.12,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若是能继续照亮我未来的方向就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:17.79,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是现在的这个自己 而是指引我找到更加优秀的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.80,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.02,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.06,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来了 你总算回来了 绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.28,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:30.45,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个人啊 欠了一大笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.31,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连夜潜逃？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.11,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁让这家伙把我们的住址也告诉人家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你们添麻烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.64,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那什么时候走？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.16,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚 好事不宜迟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然也不是什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:52.63,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讨厌啦 你以为这是谁的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.84,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也戏剧过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.20,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.13,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你鼻子很不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:04.42,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但这说不定是个改变自己的机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:08.63,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 我们去北边还是南边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:10.92,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:15.38,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么…去冷的地方的话就要买保暖内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.88,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去暖和的地方就要买连衣裙什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.94,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有带着孩子潜逃的父母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:28.58,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抛下孩子潜逃的父母才少见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:29.65,Satsuki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.63,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:47.37,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唔…我一个人去外婆家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:51.03,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高中也去那边读 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绪、绪花 别那么悲观…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:03.73,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诶？虽然从来不知道我有一个和妈妈关系不好的外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.62,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过去旅馆生活什么的 感觉好戏剧性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:12.93,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然我还是觉得夜逃更有趣些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.16,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我啊 是为了吃黏住的玉米 会往易拉罐里倒水的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.33,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 很有创意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关系最好的我占据着有利的形势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算不用着急也总有一天会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不行 我意识到我一直都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以为只要一直陪在你身边你就会在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.61,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孝 抱歉 你能说的更明白点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一直喜欢你 松前绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:57.68,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:02.87,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等、等一下 你说喜欢 那是什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:07.42,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:19.01,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果小孝居然先跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:28.28,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}车窗外的景色是心情的写照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:34.20,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本来对妈妈就不抱什么期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.85,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是想成为与从前不一样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:42.36,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是看到了和从前不一样的小孝的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:50.81,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后还是没有来送我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给 糖糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.40,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:02.27,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一直希望能遇见一位会对我说“糖糖”的老奶奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.36,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:20.14,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 我第一次见到这么大的海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.23,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刚才心情就像是在隧道里一样沉闷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:31.32,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是出了隧道还是很兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:25.50,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然有这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.45,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像电影一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.85,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杂草 不太应景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:43.50,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么难得一见的童话般的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.73,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 真的是童话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:57.58,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}美丽的女孩子对我伸出手 然后对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.04,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.21,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对我说{\3c&HF07800&\4c&HF07800&}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:10.97,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 有点意外 你能再说一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:14.73,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:21.43,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样不行啦 小民 突然对陌生人说希望他们去死这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.04,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:29.30,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 那些是小民种的野蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:32.69,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}野蒜 嗯…小民？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.90,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.51,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}野蒜小民？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.17,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是野蒜！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.47,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.40,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是绪花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:52.53,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是…外婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:54.73,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:11:00.31,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非也是会给我“糖糖”的外婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.74,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.63,SCREEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs66\blur6\pos(760,360)\bord1\c&HFDE6FF&\3c&HB727C1&}{\1a&HFF\2a&HFF\3a&HFF\4a&HFF\t(0,200,1,\1a&H00\2a&H00\3a&H00\4a&H00)}花\N{\1a&HFF\2a&HFF\3a&HFF\4a&HFF\t(150,350,1,\1a&H00\2a&H00\3a&H00\4a&H00)}开\N{\1a&HFF\2a&HFF\3a&HFF\4a&HFF\t(300,500,1,\1a&H00\2a&H00\3a&H00\4a&H00)}伊\N{\1a&HFF\2a&HFF\3a&HFF\4a&HFF\t(450,650,1,\1a&H00\2a&H00\3a&H00\4a&H00)}吕\N{\1a&HFF\2a&HFF\3a&HFF\4a&HFF\t(600,800,1,\1a&H00\2a&H00\3a&H00\4a&H00)}波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.94,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听好了 从现在开始你就是这里的工作人员了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:24.11,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作人员？我不是您外孙女吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:28.33,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫁出去的女儿生的外孙女 对我来说和猫狗没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.06,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:33.88,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 莫非我是未来的年轻的老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.62,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非也 你只是打杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.91,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非也？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.20,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高中毕业以后就随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.92,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只给你工作所得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:43.88,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:45.91,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:49.21,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好好做事的话我会扣你工资的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:53.00,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从现在起你能有吃住的地方就很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.92,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是会给我糖糖吃的奶奶比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 快到了？到了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 我知…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诶？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊？皋月姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是绪花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:26.46,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请…挪开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 真是越看越像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总是想着捉弄我的邪恶之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总是想着啮咬我的尖牙利嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.50,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…你是妈妈的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要一雪多年的怨恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.08,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是小绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.41,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.54,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有好多想问你的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.87,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皋月是怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.54,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说是个超级开放的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.09,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在家也是全裸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.20,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:20.10,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是服务生里的老大 巴 应该会成为你的前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:23.06,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会教你很多东西 作为回报你也要告诉我一些事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.61,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.39,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好炫的车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.93,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她好像是经营顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.07,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}缘真是没骨气又随便的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.49,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 果然皋月也是个随便女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.12,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好多男人追在屁股后面什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.83,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.09,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个人是豆爷爷 做清洁的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.64,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为个头小所以叫豆子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.43,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名字叫电六
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.66,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个孩子是二厨 叫做彻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.68,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}里面的那个人是这里的厨师长 莲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.55,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平头？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.98,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在是我的轮班 以后再好好给你介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:11.22,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后是… 啊 小绪花你16岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.33,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.88,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.75,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 马上就去您那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.75,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.96,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫我去死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.37,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诶？怎么 已经认识了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.57,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.73,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.29,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}认识的话就好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:30.89,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}民子菜子 既然你们三个都同年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.87,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就带她在这附近转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.61,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.18,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.26,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 菜子 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.24,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明显是被讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:58.00,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一般来说应该会安慰说“没有那种事”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:02.32,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个是我们的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:06.07,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和小民都在那里上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.01,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诶？在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.44,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你俩是在这里打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:12.00,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是打工 小民是住在这里的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:15.28,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来 她的房间里挂着制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.89,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们是同屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:17.77,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.43,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个制服很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.30,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}颜色也很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.05,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.56,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.48,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和理想中有点不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:51.29,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 本来也没有什么具体的设想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么削的这么厚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.26,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有考虑过农民伯伯的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.55,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有考虑过将削下的皮拿去炒菜的奶奶的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.44,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家是三口之家 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}动动脑子 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:13.82,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.07,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 你是老板娘的外孙女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.69,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得您说的有点过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.44,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}光对小孩子发火的话 是不会有长进的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.66,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别多管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行了 别光动嘴了 去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.01,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}厨房的事你别插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里有这里的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.93,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.51,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事情的发展变得莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.33,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过目前也没有可去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.71,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还要不要继续待下去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:09.46,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孝！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:12.62,SCREEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs65\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&HB99F9E&\move(884,617,884,570,1600,1820)}加油\h\N小绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.91,SCREEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs65\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&HB99F9E&\move(884,575,884,-60,0,1270)}加油\h\N小绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:19.88,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加油什么的 说的倒简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:30.22,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主动去联系小孝的话 还是有点难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.64,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么憧憬的戏剧般的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.12,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有点寂寞 还散发着霉味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.77,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.40,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:11.48,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比我晚睡 还比我早起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:16.54,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说那种发霉的被子根本就睡不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.22,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一 二 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.14,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.80,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.62,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事啦 请抬起头 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊是啊 只是被子掉下来了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:52.58,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绪花！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.43,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 真对不起 没注意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.81,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.68,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是万分抱气…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又没有受伤 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.87,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:12.89,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:16.68,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你跟我来 巴 去把民子也叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.18,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:23.43,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 民子的被子硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.88,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我想帮她晒一晒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.61,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就晒在客人经过的门面？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:32.97,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的 背面都是阴影 还是晒到太阳比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:38.06,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}旅馆经营是顾客至上 自己人则排在第二第三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:42.19,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 永远都排不到自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.97,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.62,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顾客当然很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:53.28,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我认为照顾好努力工作的人之类的也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.26,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.27,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}民子 过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.44,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.98,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她说就是为了晒你的被子才对顾客做了失礼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:17.75,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己周围的事自己都管不好的话怎么能行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:18.98,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.86,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.88,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:24.99,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老板娘 做错事的难道不是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:25.88,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您太不讲理了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:28.86,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是客人这样打了你 你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.95,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能轻易叫嚣人家不讲理了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.33,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做错事的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.10,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一切事情都要以顾客为中心考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:42.70,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连这样理所当然的事都做不到的话 就没有资格留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:45.93,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:50.44,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 请您也打我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:56.17,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我的过失让努力工作的人挨打 给人家添麻烦什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.10,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种事情最讨厌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.64,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十分感谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.53,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的 真的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.37,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.08,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么 我又没在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.66,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不敢相信呢 老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.85,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她说的话都好奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:32.53,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让人不敢相信的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:37.09,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你把旅馆…把工作当什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:44.83,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这…我也不是来这里工作的 再说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:45.67,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.31,Minko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:56.90,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再次 被人希望去死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很投入嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 我是缘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:12.24,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又不是想工作才来这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:15.21,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:31.04,Ohana,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不甘心 我不甘心
