Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an1}叫老板娘来！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:04.85,Nako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要让她发泄一下才行
