Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:06.30,Tomoe,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8\fs42}不带你这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:05.31,Sui,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an1}叫警察来吧
